%% Model Registry - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.2/model-registry.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/SDK)
    participant Gateway as Istio kubeflow-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Proxy as Model Registry Proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Istio mTLS
    participant MySQL as MySQL 8.3+<br/>3306/TCP<br/>Configurable TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as K8s API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as InferenceService<br/>Controller
    participant CSIInit as CSI Storage<br/>Initializer
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/OCI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CatalogSrv as Catalog Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PgSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,MySQL: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, User credentials
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080, Istio mTLS, Peer certificate
    Proxy->>MySQL: INSERT model metadata<br/>MySQL/3306, Configurable TLS 1.2+, DB credentials
    MySQL-->>Proxy: Confirmation
    Proxy-->>Gateway: 201 Created (JSON)
    Gateway-->>Client: Response

    Note over K8sAPI,MySQL: Flow 2: InferenceService Sync (Controller)
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch stream: InferenceService events<br/>TLS, ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>Proxy: PUT /inference_services<br/>HTTP/8080, Configurable, Bearer Token (optional)
    Proxy->>MySQL: UPDATE inference service metadata<br/>MySQL/3306
    MySQL-->>Proxy: Confirmation
    Proxy-->>Controller: 200 OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH InferenceService status<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, SA token

    Note over CSIInit,Storage: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
    CSIInit->>Proxy: GET model artifact URI<br/>HTTP/8080, plaintext
    Proxy-->>CSIInit: model-registry:// URI + storage location
    CSIInit->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, Storage credentials
    Storage-->>CSIInit: Model artifacts

    Note over CatalogSrv,HF: Flow 4: Model Catalog Source Loading
    CatalogSrv->>PgSQL: Initialize catalog schema<br/>PostgreSQL/5432, DB credentials
    PgSQL-->>CatalogSrv: Ready
    CatalogSrv->>HF: Fetch model metadata<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS, API Key (optional)
    HF-->>CatalogSrv: Model catalog data
    CatalogSrv->>PgSQL: Store catalog entries<br/>PostgreSQL/5432
